PN,39201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,FThe chairman of a Manchester mosque
OL,7,Fhas asked for increased police
OL,8,Fpresence after what the Prime Minister
OL,9,Fcalled a "concerning" incident when an
OL,10,Farmed man arrived during Ramadan
OL,11,Fprayers.
OL,13,FHammad Khan spoke after the arrest of
OL,14,Fa white man in his 50s, who had gone
OL,15,Finto Manchester Central Mosque wearing
OL,16,Fhi-vis and had with him an axe, knife
OL,17,Fand hammer.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police say they
OL,7,Fhave not declared it a terrorist
OL,8,Fincident but are working with Counter
OL,9,FTerrorism Police to investigate.
OL,11,FThe suspect is being held on suspicion
OL,12,Fof possessing an offensive weapon and
OL,13,Fclass B drugs.
OL,15,FA second man, a black male, who is
OL,16,Fbelieved to have been with the suspect
OL,17,Fbut left before officers arrived, is
OL,18,Fnow being hunted by police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,FMr Khan said volunteers kept the
OL,7,Fsuspect talking until police arrived
OL,8,Fand arrested him, where he shouted,
OL,9,F"I'm not a terrorist!" according to
OL,10,Fone man who was present as he was
OL,11,Ftaken away.
OL,13,FMr Khan said the suspect was "very
OL,14,Fcalm" and had been spotted visiting
OL,15,Fthe mosque, in the Victoria Park area
OL,16,Fof south Manchester, before last night.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]uD@^OUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,FHowever, after entering the mosque
OL,7,Faround 8.30pm on Tuesday 24 February,
OL,8,Fwhere around 1,500 people were saying
OL,9,FRamadan prayers, an axe was spotted in
OL,10,Fhis bag and he was ushered into an
OL,11,Foffice by volunteers and police called.
OL,13,FHe had a knife and a hammer on him,
OL,14,Falong with "other materials" relating
OL,15,Fto the Second World War and some
OL,16,Fnewspaper cuttings.
OL,18,FMr Khan added: "His demeanour was very
OL,19,Fcalm.
OL,26,@vD@LOUvD@\O]zD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"He wasn't under the influence of
OL,7,Fanything at all. I also understand he
OL,8,Fwas also carrying some other materials
OL,9,Fwith him relating to World War Two,
OL,10,Falso some newspaper cuttings, which
OL,11,Fthe police have.
OL,13,F"The volunteers obviously kept the
OL,14,Fconversation going in very amenable
OL,15,Fway to ensure the situation did not
OL,16,Fescalate in any way."
OL,18,FMr Khan said he had asked police for
OL,19,Fan increased police presence around
OL,20,Fall the local mosques after an
OL,21,Fincrease in hate mail and threats.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,FHe added: "I was disappointed that we
OL,7,Fdidn't have visible presence.
OL,9,F"I stressed prior to the month of
OL,10,FRamadan we needed police presence
OL,11,Fbecause prayers go on to late at
OL,12,Fnight."
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer said: "I am concerned
OL,15,Fto hear of the incident at Manchester
OL,16,FCentral Mosque last night.
OL,18,F"I know this will be worrying for
OL,19,FMuslim communities, especially during
OL,20,FRamadan, a time of peace and
OL,21,Freflection.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@AOUtD@GO]vD@XOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"My thanks go to the volunteers and
OL,7,Femergency services for their quick
OL,8,Fresponse.
OL,10,F"We have provided up to #40 million
OL,11,Ffunding for additional security at
OL,12,Fmosques, Muslim schools and community
OL,13,Fcentres, and will continue to act to
OL,14,Fensure communities are able to live
OL,15,Fwithout fear."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,FIn a statement, the mosque said a
OL,7,F"serious security incident" had
OL,8,Foccurred during prayers and the Muslim
OL,9,Fcommunity more generally had
OL,10,Fexperienced a rise in threats and
OL,11,Fhostility in recent years.
OL,13,FAssistant Chief Constable John
OL,14,FWebster, from Greater Manchester
OL,15,FPolice (GMP) said: "We were called at
OL,16,Faround 8.40pm to concern from security
OL,17,Fstaff at the mosque about a white man
OL,18,Fin a high-vis jacket carrying a bag
OL,19,Fwith an axe inside.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@[O]wD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"The man had reportedly claimed to be
OL,7,Fin the mosque to do work on the
OL,8,Fbuilding, but staff had no knowledge
OL,9,Fof this.
OL,11,F"They rightly acted on their
OL,12,Fsuspicions and called police.
OL,14,F"There was no suggestion that he made
OL,15,Fany threats or confronted members of
OL,16,Fthe congregation.
OL,18,F"However, we understand the concern
OL,19,Fthat this suspicious and concerning
OL,20,Fbehaviour caused.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"We quickly responded to the scene
OL,7,Fwhere we searched the suspect,
OL,8,Farrested him and seized weapons,
OL,9,Fincluding an axe, a knife and class B
OL,10,Fdrugs.
OL,12,F"The suspect, a white man in his 50s,
OL,13,Fis under arrest on suspicion of
OL,14,Fpossessing an offensive weapon and
OL,15,Fclass B drugs.
OL,17,F"At this time, it is not clear what
OL,18,Fthe circumstances or intent, if any,
OL,19,Fwas around this incident.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"I know this uncertainty can cause
OL,7,Fconcern, but it is key that we have
OL,8,Fthe time to question the suspect and
OL,9,Fspeak to as many witnesses as possible
OL,10,Fto understand the nature of this
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,F"To ensure we are appropriately
OL,14,Fexploring every line of inquiry, we
OL,15,Fare working with detectives from
OL,16,FCounter Terrorism Policing North West,
OL,17,Fbut it has not been declared a
OL,18,Fterrorist incident.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"We are taking this very seriously and
OL,7,Fhave increased patrols around mosques
OL,8,Fat what we know is a really important
OL,9,Ftime for Muslim communities as they
OL,10,Fcome together during Ramadan.
OL,12,F"We're reviewing all available CCTV
OL,13,Fand body-worn video to identify a
OL,14,Fsecond man, a black man, who was
OL,15,Freported as acting suspiciously in the
OL,16,Fmosque at the same time as the suspect.
OL,18,F"He is described as approximately in
OL,19,Fhis late 40s, with an athletic build
OL,20,Fand short stubbled facial hair.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"He was wearing a grey hoody with the
OL,7,Fhood up, a navy blue jacket with that
OL,8,Fhood also up (double hood), blue
OL,9,Ftracksuit bottoms, and white trainers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,FIn a statement outside Manchester
OL,7,FCentral Mosque on Wednesday evening,
OL,8,FGreater Manchester mayor Andy Burnham
OL,9,Fsaid: "We know that this incident is a
OL,10,Fhuge cause of concern for those,
OL,11,Fobviously, who were present at the
OL,12,Fmosque last night, for people living
OL,13,Fin this community who worship here,
OL,14,Fbut, of course, to the Muslim
OL,15,Fcommunity across Greater Manchester,
OL,16,Fparticularly happening as it did in
OL,17,Fthis holy time of Ramadan.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"So, tonight, we wanted to come down
OL,7,Fto listen, but also, as much as we
OL,8,Fcould, to provide some reassurance
OL,9,Fthat the whole of the Greater
OL,10,FManchester community is working to
OL,11,Fsupport colleagues here at this time,
OL,12,Fand make sure we fully understand and
OL,13,Finvestigate what's happened.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772093097
OL,3,CCall for more police help from
OL,4,CManchester mosque after axe incident
OL,6,F"Everybody in our city region, whoever
OL,7,Fthey are, whatever faith they follow,
OL,8,Fshould be free at all times to
OL,9,Fpractice that faith, to worship in
OL,10,Ftheir communities, and we will never
OL,11,Faccept a city region where people have
OL,12,Fany fear of being at their place of
OL,13,Fworship, and that's why we're working
OL,14,Fwith Greater Manchester Police to
OL,15,Fstrengthen security at places of
OL,16,Fworship as much as we possibly can."
OL,18,FAnyone with information is urged to
OL,19,Fcontact GMP on 101 or through the
OL,20,FLiveChat function on the force's
OL,21,Fwebsite.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
